new zealand retail sale slow in januari season adjust retail sale rose by 0.1 pct in januari , compar with increas of 5.7 pct in decemb and 1.0 pct a year earlier , the statist depart said . it said in a statement actual retail sale fell to 1.87 billion n.z . dlr in januari against 2.42 billion a month earlier and compar with 1.78 billion in januari 1986. year-on-year retail sale rose 5.3 pct compar with a 9.6 pct increas in the year-earli period .